<i>noun</i>: 숨구멍 [숨ː꾸멍] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>숨구멍 [숨ː꾸멍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. fontanelle; soft spot</dd><br>
<dd>갓난아이의 정수리에 있는, 굳지 않아서 숨 쉴 때마다 발딱발딱 뛰는 부분.</dd><br>
<dd>The soft part on the crown of a newborn baby, which throbs whenever he/she breathes.</dd><br>
<dd>2. breath</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 답답한 상황에서 조금이나마 벗어나게 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state of being temporarily relieved from a frustrating situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>